{"tid":1533490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得勸交撚好煩？","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:47:21.000Z","uid":298978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3504a48d7de5e254386c7d88aad5e1a240e73574","tid":1533490,"uid":298978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好打啦！唔好打啦！唔好打啦！</span></span><br />\n次次幾經辛苦捉到人落單，就有班人阻住哂！喂！你係手足就睇水開遮啦！<br />\n唔係我讚對家，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但對家真係有先見之明！</span> 一早開咪叫我地做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">曱甴</span></span><br />\n納粹德軍屠殺猶太人果時都係叫猶太人做曱甴先殺得咁狠！而家對家連廢佬都叫，邊叫邊出手打！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">所以要諗方法消除大家對&ldquo;打人&rdquo;既心理關口</span></span>，此關一破，200萬點會輸比3萬？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我哋要以其人之道還其狗之身！咩黑警，廢佬都係同人有關，點都唔夠咁曱甴咁&ldquo;易殺，煩，害蟲&rdquo;，要有齊三個共通點，而且有少少人開始話黑警既就係&ldquo;老鼠&rdquo;。其實真係唔洗諗其他，簡單直接！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">以後對家就叫老鼠</span></span><br />\n要追返比人叫曱甴既差距，叫到自己人都認為黑警藍絲都係老鼠，我以後唔想再係前線見到勸交撚！"},{"pid":"ebc32d585f1b9740b86d68b842f433779eb0986e","tid":1533490,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"好撚攰呀，依加仲未有Twitter個啲我屌你老母，手足打生打死，你禁幾個制都唔肯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533413</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組係文，我地係宣<br />\n有文無宣食得屎"},{"pid":"7178ffd87865f284c01019257266c80cd4d8e348","tid":1533490,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"入黎了解真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［整合］聽日早上7點 光復大埔何郭佩珍中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b49359ce2f457b8fb5b504b3817c04233a28a0a6","tid":1533490,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"無記者就住死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262a1bb15a55dae475792becbe46e5d4d2d7ace7","tid":1533490,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}